premise_source_doc_sentence: Although Cheers ended ambiguously with regard to Frasier and Lilith 's marriage , at the beginning of the spin-off series Frasier , their divorce had been finalized , with Lilith gaining custody of Frederick and remaining in Boston while Frasier has moved back to his hometown of Seattle .
Sideshow Bob shares some personality traits of Grammer 's character Frasier Crane from the sitcoms Cheers and Frasier , and has been described as `` Frasier pickled in arsenic '' .
Unlike Frasier , part of whose background comes from Cheers , Niles ' background is established over the course of Frasier .

Several parallels have been explicitly drawn in The Simpsons between Bob and Frasier Crane -- Bob 's brother Cecil and his father were played by David Hyde Pierce and John Mahoney respectively , echoing the roles they played in Frasier .

Frasier quickly learns from his anal retentive younger brother Niles  (  David Hyde-Pierce  )  that their disabled father Martin  (  John Mahoney  )  is no longer able to live alone and Frasier reluctantly agrees to take him in  (  along with Martin 's favorite recliner and his dog , Eddie  (  Moose  )   )  .
